{"tid":868556,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"為吸客有幾盡？嘉豐花園放盤劈近200萬　再送50萬裝修","createTime":"2018-10-19T14:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T18:59:30.000Z","uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"61b20c7511406c4ceaf860d422bea31e6f089ca2","tid":868556,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"10月19日(五) 17:53<br />\n<br />\n二手樓市勁靜，加上新盤付款優惠多搶客，個別業主除劈價亦出招。美聯梁榮貴表示，大埔嘉豐花園有一個實用面積1,042方呎單位，原業主購入收租多年，近兩星期交吉後收回放售，最初連車位叫價1,300萬元，市況淡靜，近日已降價至1,102萬元，但業主心感未來樓價都會下跌，不如盡快套現，決定再送50萬元裝修，新買家可選擇樓價中扣除，或完成交易後收取現金。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，上址車位市值約100萬元，約扣除50萬元裝修費，每方呎叫價已低於1萬元，當中未計及額外議價空間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181019/photo/bkn-20181019175347951-1019_00842_001_01b.jpg?20181019180745\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181019%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181019175347951-1019_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20181019180745&h=de77aed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181019/bkn-20181019175347951-1019_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181019%2Fbkn-20181019175347951-1019_00842_001.html&d=BpnPxQCMLZFFl5rQmDXvrWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=02b0db11\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181019/bkn-20181019175347951-1019_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"46c8772d23373af03de6a0421a67645bc025f82d","tid":868556,"uid":199370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"低處未算低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c51e2281ec0f54167d73401f7deff16e09ff1d","tid":868556,"uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:43:39.000Z","msg":"呢個業主要向低置業主學野<br />\n<br />\n緊係反價, 一係放租加租"},{"pid":"c3732660628162dcf25595340e0343f0636f5421","tid":868556,"uid":28245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"